  <section id="about"><div class="si">
    <div class="sh rv"><div class="sl">// About</div><h2 class="st">The operator behind the portfolio</h2><p class="sd">Operational systems by day, launch-ready tooling after hours, with the same bias toward calm, reliable software in both places.</p></div>
    <div class="ac">
